"<dt><a href='#Section1'>Hypothyroidism, central</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section1'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> FatigueDepressionCold intoleranceExcessive sleepinessDry, coarse hairConstipationDry skinMuscle crampsDecreased concentration.",
