"<dt><a href='#Section2'>Cushing's syndrome</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section2'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Central obesityMoon faciesStriaeHirsutismLipodystrophyHypertensionDiabetesDepression.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Urinary free cortisol level: &gt;50 micrograms/24 hoursLow-dose dexamethasone suppression test: morning serum cortisol &gt;50 nanomol/L (&gt;1.8 micrograms/dL)The presence of obesity may give false-positive results. If suspected, should be confirmed with further testing.</p>",
